dialogue.text: Babe, where are you going..?
I have a headache. I'm gonna go get some water, that's all.
A headache? Are you alright BF...?
Yeah... I'm ok, Im just gonna go grab a cup of water real quick so that it could go away.
Oh and we have to go to the theater today. I bet your dad is already there...
WAIT WHAT TIME IS IT?
It's like 7:40 in the morning, I don't know what time we gotta be there by.
We have to be there by 8:00!!
WHAT!! THAT EARLY?! WHY DOES HE WANT US THERE BY 8:00?!
I DON'T KNOW WHY BF, BUT WE GOTTA GO NOW, Come on!
(Well great. I shouldn't have said anything about that otherwise this wouldn't have happen to me in the first place.)
(BF and GF were running to the theater as fast as possible as to not be late)
GF... (huff) You do realize we can be just a little 10 minutes late!?
No! This is huge for me!
(BF and GF head in the theater and see Daddy Dearest fixing up GF's Speakers)
Dad? What are you doing to my speakers?
Dad: oh... GF, I'm just fixing it after last time me and your little Boyfriend battled.
You do realize I've been through so many places with those speakers right?
Dad: It didn't work earlier so I'm just fixing it up before our battle.
Oh ok :) (she smiled at BF)
(He looks back at GF and Daddy Dearest) Do I really have to be here? If we're rap battling again, I am easily gonna win.
Dad: Yes, you have to be here since we have to do another rap battle because I want a rematch after what happened before.
(sigh) Fine, lets just get this over with. You're going down.
(A new remix on the speakers begins to play for 5 seconds)
EEEE!!! I can't wait! (She was excited to watch Daddy Dearest and BF battle)
Hello there, I am the one that created the entire dialogue for the mod so far at the moment.
The extra lines added to the dialogue will possibly be added depending if the owner of the mod would like to add them or not.
For the line of GF 'EEEE I can't wait!! (the ones after that line and etc will not be shown in the mod.
Well... while your here, I guess I'll introduce myself and who made this anyways.
The name's Nixvyy and I am one of the devs for the Friday Night Funkin SkyDecay Mod.
I have a few roles in the mod such as Voice Acting, Beta Testing, and Dialogue Editing :D
I will be Voice Acting for BF within the mod meaning I will have a crap ton of lines to say. (I also might have my custom one as a playable character in the mod maybe)
I have been working on this dialogue for about 2 hours or maybe more, Im not too sure but shows how determined I was lol.
I literally stayed up until 1:24 AM just to get this dialogue finished and placed in the Dialogue Folder to be used within the mod.
The bad thing about that is I have to create dialogue for so many songs which is gonna be difficult due to school and such.
So the dialogue will have to wait until I am either on break or so.
Mid-Term Exam's and Finals might slow me down as I will need to study for them so I can be on summer break and continue working on the mod.
Alright now enough of that, I know what your thinking, What will this FNF mod be about anyways. Can you tell me a bit about it? Well yes I can.
This mod features a twitch streamer known as Josephjr05 (the person streaming right now)
It takes place in the Week 1 Theater with Daddy Dearest was is relatively the beginning of the story which is known as Chapter 1.
It also features a Blue Orb that has took everything from BF's World and started to destroy his universe.
BF, GF, and Pico travel through different universes due to the Orb's Power.
The worlds of BF and Joseph's were mixed up and everything becomes weird in their world.
Joseph and his crewman are on a mission to find out why this is happening to them since they have been researching this for 20 years.
BF, GF, and Pico meet Joseph and they work together to put a stop to this Orb and restore peace to their worlds.
Ok now for the extra stuff about the mod. You may be wondering what this mod will have stored for the FNF community.
There will be 15 Chapters of the mod possibly containing either 3-4 songs, Mechanics and Modcharts.
Easy, Normal, Hard, Advanced, Insane, Expert, Maximum, and Mania Difficulties.
Harder Difficulties are NOT to be taken seriously as these are for Osu!mania players but don't worry as that will only be available via Mania Difficulty or something idrk.
The charting on the songs may be changed depending on if we wanna make it a bit easier to do.
This mod is currently in its Demo or Beta Build at the moment so there will be a lot of things changed from the Demo of it.
The dev team and Joseph are not sure of the exact release date of the mod but we hope to get it out by atleast 2023 or 2024.
Also about the charting and how I said I had no experience, one of the songs Funk-Off did not have its chart finished so I decided to finish it and send the finished to Joseph.
Ummmmm, I ran out of things I wanted to say because I'm tired so ima leave it there.
I wanna thank you for your time and listening to what I had to say, I am very thankful.
Anyways, I should be on my way now and go to sleep since I don't want to be sleep deprived.
Just one more final thing, I am Joseph's twitch moderator on his stream. The username is thelegendbro736.
So if you decide to see me, feel free to say Hi to me in the twitch chat.
Alright now im actually gonna go to sleep now, Goodbye everyone.
(End of Dialogue)
